    "date": "2022-08-08T16:50:00Z",
    "text": "Cultivating Organic Matter through the Promotion Of Sustainable Techniques Act or the COMPOST Act\n\nThis bill makes composting a conservation practice for purposes of Department of Agriculture (USDA) conservation programs. The bill also requires USDA to establish a competitive program to award grants and loan guarantees for projects that expand access to food waste composting."
